=== Least Privilege Verification ===

Test 1: Access a bucket never granted in the policy
Command: aws s3 ls s3://some-other-bucket-name/
Result: AccessDenied - correctly blocked, as expected. The role's policy
only grants access to ce-bootcamp-m2-05-balint specifically.

Test 2: Attempt an action never granted (delete), even on the correct bucket
Command: aws s3 rb s3://ce-bootcamp-m2-05-balint --force
Result: AccessDenied - correctly blocked, as expected. The policy grants
GetObject, PutObject, and ListBucket only - never DeleteBucket or
DeleteObject.

Both failures confirm the role enforces least privilege correctly: it can
only do what was explicitly granted, and nothing more, even on resources
it otherwise has access to.

